# No-show - Health Analysis Project
Data: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/joniarroba/noshowappointments?resource=download

## Overview
Analysis of patient appointment no-show rates using a public dataset. Explored patterns by:
- Neighborhood
- Appointment weekday
- Scheduled hour

## Tools
- Python (Pandas, Matplotlib)
- Jupyter Notebook

## Key Findings
- Certain neighborhoods and weekdays have higher no-show rates.
- Scheduled time of day influences likelihood of attending.

## Notes
- Cleaned and processed dates, handled missing data, created flags, pivoted tables, and generated visualizations.
